Here is the complete code for Aura Tasks, the ultimate minimalist and intelligent task application.
It features:
Aura AI Engine: A simulated NLP engine that parses natural language inputs (e.g., "Llamar a RaÃºl maÃ±ana urgente") to auto-assign dates, priorities, and types.
